_sText: This is a surf map i made quite a while ago for me and my brother, never really got around to uploading it. so... here it is :D surf_MorningGlory. its a medium sized surf map which would be a good map with more players on i think, which is why im uploading it. there are a good few secrets on it too ;D i think it's 100% done now, minus the textures, sooooo. enjoy :D
